<http://drug.uk/usage/hepatic-impairment/cbf07a1a-d289-488d-ab90-9006d0d7f1b5> <http://drug.uk/model/patientCondition> "HepaticImpairment" .
<http://drug.uk/usage/hepatic-impairment/cbf07a1a-d289-488d-ab90-9006d0d7f1b5> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " With systemic use:\nManufacturer advises caution in severe impairment (risk of increased exposure).\nDose adjustments\nWith systemic use:\nManufacturer advises consider dose reduction in severe impairment to maintain blood-ciclosporin concentration in target range—monitor until concentration stable." .
<http://drug.uk/usage/hepatic-impairment/cbf07a1a-d289-488d-ab90-9006d0d7f1b5> <http://drug.uk/model/safetyLevel> "caution" .
